message:
Happy Friday from your WinCon Fireseeds (part two)!!!

We have two more reminders for you:

1. please please please register under Minneapolis

2. You do not have to put down any more than $39 when you register. You can finish payment at the Hilton on the 28th (at the latest!) if you'd like, or edit your registration to pay online at some other time

Go register!
